Class LevelBoss

java.lang.Object
java.util.Observable
com.example.demo.levels.LevelParent
com.example.demo.levels.LevelBoss
public class LevelBoss extends LevelParent
LevelBoss manages the boss encounter, including boss behavior, health display, and player interaction during the final level.
